summary: This is an email forwarding a batch of FBI 302 interview reports (specifically part 3 of 3) related to the Epstein investigation. The email indicates that a significant interview ends in document 377.
keyFacts: The email forwards a batch of FBI 302 interview reports (part 3 of 3) related to the Epstein investigation.
The attached documents are FBI 302 forms, which are official reports of interviews conducted by FBI agents.
The email specifically notes that a significant interview is included in this batch and ends in document 377.
The email chain dates to April 22-23, 2020, indicating ongoing investigative activity at that time.
